name: Marmol #3
description:
Marmol #3 is part of a series of 4 images.

Marmol #3 was algorithmically generated with Python creating a random color with unknown seed.

The color of each pixel is calculated as an average of the color of the adjacent top and left pixels.

Then, again randomly, a value between -3 and 3 is added to each RGB component.

2048 x 2048 px.
